Materials Required:

1.	Breadboard
2.	Esp32 - (helpful site: https://hackaday.io/project/167346/instructions)
3.	Soil Moisture Sensor (with PM-WCS-3 ) - https://tinovi.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/PM-WCS-3-I2C.pdf
4.	4 channel Arduino relay 
5.	Load cell with xfw-hx711 - https://www.instructables.com/How-to-Interface-HX711-Balance-Module-With-Load-Ce/
6.	Solenoid valve
7.	Terminal Strips and Screw Terminals
8.	Basic tools and Soldering Kit
9.	Tears, sweat, and burns

